Enum TouchHandler

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TouchHandler>
    public enum TouchHandler
extends java.lang.Enum<TouchHandler>
    The TouchHandler is a utility to handle the touch event about the frog.

    Note: this class is a singleton with Enum.
